description:
What was the road like that Abraham travelled on the way to Canaan, as he passed through pagan territories? What does Canaan mean for us today? Compare Abraham’s religion with the pagan religions of his day. Abraham’s religion conveyed a message to the heathen nations about a God of love, willing to die for sinners to save them. Visit the sites where Abraham heard God speak. Francois DuPlessis presents Abraham's journey from Ur to Canaan while sharing with us the lessons we can learn from his journey. 

Watch more: https://adtv.watch/

Subscribe to our YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/OfficialADTVChannel?sub_confirmation=1

Visit our website: https://new.amazingdiscoveries.org/
